INSERT INTO tbl_news VALUES('3','从4月6日起，英国对外留学生新签证政策正式实施','1428336000','upload/20151209/20151209151350_99181.jpg','','<p style=\"margin-left:0cm;text-indent:17.55pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;\">据中国之声《新闻纵横》报道，英国的一项新政将影响到很多中国家庭。数据显示，目前在英国留学的中国学生已经达到了13万，其中约有95000名学生在英国接受高等教育。去年，有58810名中国籍留学生在英国开始了本科阶段的学习，比来自非英国的欧盟国家的新生人数总和还多。英国的这项签证新政，影响的正是这些人。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;\">从4月6日起，英国对外留学生新签证政策正式实施。对于准备赴英的留学生来说，最大的变动就在于雅思考试。这项新的留学签证政策多出一种签证类雅思考试，虽然和普通雅思考试相比，从考试内容、形式、难度等级等方面完全相同，但是这类考试中国大陆地区只有12个考场，考位紧缺，一旦报不上名，就去不成英国。于是，这项突然宣布的新政策令很多学生措手不及，国内留学中介机构也没有事先预料。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#000000;\">那么，英国为什么突然颁布这项措施？将对即将赴英留学生造成什么影响？</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;\">根据新的留学签证，准备赴英国留学的学生如果在4月6号之后参加雅思考试，必须参加IELTS for UKVI，中国称之为签证类雅思考试，英国方面将不承认其他语言成绩，包括普通雅思成绩。目前，在4月6号之前，已经考出符合入学要求的普通雅思考试成绩仍然有效。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#000000;\">那么，这个新出的签证类雅思考试与普通雅思考试有什么区别呢</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color:#000000;\">?</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;\">首先，签证类雅思考点安全监控技术和级别更高。其次，考点在中国大陆地区目前只提供12处考点，其中，北京只有一个，就是北京外国语大学考点。第三，考试费用更高，普通雅思考试一次1450元，签证类雅思考试一次2000元。这就意味着，如果有学生已经在除北京外国语大学以外的其他考点报名了4月6号以后的考试，那么就不属于签证类雅思考试，这部分同学面临之前报名作废，需要重新报名的情况。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;\">新政策的紧缩不仅体现在对雅思考试的要求上，对时限也有更严格限制。以往学生只要考出符合硕士正课入学要求，即不需要读语言的雅思成绩，就可以直接拿到所需学制再加半年的签证。新政之后，这类学生只能先拿到一个30天的临时签证，要求留学生到达英国的10天之内办理生物识别卡来延长签证，如果超过10天，签证就作废。另外，原本英国对留学生提供的免费医疗服务是赴英留学生津津乐道的事，一分钱医疗费都不用交可以享受全额免费医疗。而现在免费医疗虽照样可享受，但留学生需要交150镑的医疗保险费。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#000000;\">留英签证新政真的会让很多学生对英国留学说不吗？如果舍弃英国，你又会选择去哪里留学呢？</span> \r\n</p>','1','1','0');
INSERT INTO tbl_news VALUES('4','英国留学签证三大新政策之“BID卡” ','1428336000','upload/20151209/20151209171627_59831.jpg','','<p style=\"margin-left:0cm;text-indent:17.55pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\">2015</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;color:#3E3E3E;\">年绝对是英国非常繁忙的一年，因为英国大选的举行，使得很多国家政策都开始更新、改变。而最令英国留学童鞋关心的英国留学签证政策也发生了巨大的变化。</span><span style=\"text-indent:17.55pt;font-size:9pt;line-height:1.5;color:#3E3E3E;\">下面，就让我们一起来了解一下英国留学签证的</span><span color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\" style=\"text-indent: 17.55pt; font-size: 9pt; line-height: 1.5;\">BID</span><span style=\"text-indent:17.55pt;font-size:9pt;line-height:1.5;color:#3E3E3E;\">卡。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm;text-indent:17.55pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;color:#3E3E3E;\">从今年</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;color:#3E3E3E;\">月起，凡是在英国境外申请超过</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;color:#3E3E3E;\">个月签证的申请人，仍将获得一张纸质签证，但是</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;color:#3E3E3E;\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;color:#3E3E3E;\">号新的签证政策规定，签证一旦生效，申请人会收到一封确认函和一个允许在英国逗留</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\">30</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;color:#3E3E3E;\">天的临时签证。</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm;text-indent:17.55pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;color:#3E3E3E;\">抵达英国之后，</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\">10</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;color:#3E3E3E;\">天之内到指定的邮局领取</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\">“BID(Biometric Identity Document</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;color:#3E3E3E;\">生物指纹识别卡</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\">)”</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;color:#3E3E3E;\">，逾期不取卡的，签证将会作废。</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm;text-indent:17.55pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;color:#3E3E3E;\">就是现在申请新的英国签证都是需要按手印，签证也从纸签证变成了一张</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\">ID</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;color:#3E3E3E;\">卡，被称作</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\">Biometric Residence Permit</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;color:#3E3E3E;\">，这张卡会包含你的指纹及签证信息。</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm;text-indent:17.55pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;color:#3E3E3E;\">面签是当天直接按手印照相片。</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm;text-indent:17.55pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;color:#3E3E3E;\">在英国邮寄申请的话，收到申请表后</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\">UKBA</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;color:#3E3E3E;\">会给你寄信让你去附近可以按手印的地方，过程只需</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\">10</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;color:#3E3E3E;\">分钟。</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm;text-indent:17.55pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;color:#3E3E3E;\">手印按完</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\">ID</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;color:#3E3E3E;\">卡是不会当天给你的。如果你是在英国境内办签证卡，通过的话</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\">ID</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;color:#3E3E3E;\">卡会寄到你家。</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm;text-indent:17.55pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;color:#3E3E3E;\">如果你是在英国以外办的，那就来了之后去邮局取就好了。</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm;text-indent:17.55pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;color:#3E3E3E;\"><strong>出现</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\"><strong>Bug</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;color:#3E3E3E;\"><strong>怎么破？</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm;text-indent:17.55pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;color:#3E3E3E;\">如果遇到各种</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\">Bug</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;color:#3E3E3E;\">，比如在按手印后的十个工作日后还没有收到你的</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\">ID</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;color:#3E3E3E;\">卡，或者</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\">ID</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;color:#3E3E3E;\">卡上的信息</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;color:#3E3E3E;\">比如名字，出生年月等</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\">)</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;color:#3E3E3E;\">不正确，或者你的</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\">ID</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;color:#3E3E3E;\">卡丢失了需要补办，也不要慌张，发邮件联系相关部门就好。</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm;text-indent:17.55pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;color:#3E3E3E;\">该政策的实施会对留英学生带来多大的影响呢？小编以为，这样做进一步繁琐了签证的办理，但是只要童鞋们在规定时间内获取</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\">BID</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;color:#3E3E3E;\">卡，应该不会有太大的麻烦。但是未来究竟会怎样呢，还是让我们拭目以待吧。</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>','1','1','0');
INSERT INTO tbl_news VALUES('5',' 英国留学打工：中国城VS英国店','1428508800','upload/20151209/20151209172141_63270.jpg','','<p style=\"text-indent:18.0pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:9pt;\"> </span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">有不少同学去英国留学的时候都选择了做一些零工，这样积累经验的同时还能缓解一部分经济压力，那么有什么适合英国留学生工作的地方呢</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">?</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">百利天下留学为大家好好说道说道。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<strong style=\"font-size:9pt;text-indent:18pt;line-height:1.5;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:宋体;border:1pt none windowtext;padding:0cm;\"><br />\r\n</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<strong style=\"font-size:9pt;text-indent:18pt;line-height:1.5;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:宋体;border:1pt none windowtext;padding:0cm;color:#337FE5;line-height:1.5;\">中国城打工情况</span></strong><strong style=\"font-size:9pt;text-indent:18pt;line-height:1.5;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;border:1pt none windowtext;padding:0cm;color:#337FE5;line-height:1.5;\">:</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">这一类的英国留学生打工的特点是工资高，不用交税</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">所以也不用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">NI)</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">。有的人这样打工打了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">年，所有学费，生活费全部自给自足。但是这类工资也是很消耗体力的，有的女孩子刚干了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">个晚上就挺不住了。另外，会说粤语也是很重要的，不过北方的朋友们不必担心，粤语并不难学。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">1</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">、中国城餐馆侍者</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">收入：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">镑</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">50-7</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">镑每小时</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">+</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">小费</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">有些餐馆的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">PART TIME </span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">不能拿小费〕</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">缺点：夜工多，特别消耗体力，需要会说一定的粤语。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">优点：不用交税，不用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">NI</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">，可以有一定的口语锻炼机会。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">备注：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">侍者分上菜和写单两种，前者对粤语要求不高，但是工资基本在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">镑以下，后者因为要和厨师交流，需要很强的粤语能力。同时可称得上是骨干，受老板青睐者工资可以达到十镑每小时</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">+</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">小费〕他们的工资水平让英国部门经理级的职员都羡慕不已，在英国自己挣钱买车的基本上都是这些人。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">2</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">、外卖店收银</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">收入：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">镑</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">-5</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">镑每小时。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">缺点：所有工作时间必须站立，老板一般不喜欢你用计算器，要有很强的心算能力，对英国留学生英语能力要求较高，需要能听懂定餐电话。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">优点：不用交税，不用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">NI</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">，体力消耗小于餐厅侍者，比较锻炼口语和听力</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\"> (</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">尤其是接电话能力〕。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">　　</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\"><span style=\"color:#337FE5;\">英国店打工</span><span style=\"color:#337FE5;\">情况：</span></span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">到英国人的地盘去打工，这一部分的收入相差不大，优点是可以有更多的机会练习口语和交流能力。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"text-indent:18pt;line-height:1.5;\"><strong>缺点</strong>是：需要英国留学生有较强的英语能力，需要申请</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-indent:18pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">NI</span><span style=\"text-indent:18pt;line-height:1.5;\">和交税。占收入</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-indent:18pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">22%</span><span style=\"text-indent:18pt;line-height:1.5;\">的税要交给英国政府，而且除了有孩子的能拿到育儿津贴之外不能享受任何福利待遇。就连价钱比较便宜的政府补贴的公众公寓都不能住。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-indent:18pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">(</span><span style=\"text-indent:18pt;line-height:1.5;\">工资皆为税前收入，税由雇主代扣，英国政府在放宽外国学生打工限制的同时也规定我们不能再向以前那样享受免税待遇，凡是年资收入</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-indent:18pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">4535</span><span style=\"text-indent:18pt;line-height:1.5;\">镑的必须交税，而大部分雇主不管你在他那干多久，也不管你一年能挣多少一律扣</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-indent:18pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">22%</span><span style=\"text-indent:18pt;line-height:1.5;\">的税〕写到这里情不自禁开始唱国际歌。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">、酒吧调酒师</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">收入：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">镑</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">50</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">便士</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">-8</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">镑</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\"> (</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">经验是必须的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">);</span><o:p></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">、酒店房间整理</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">收入：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">镑</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">30</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">便士</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">-5</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">镑</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">50</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">便士</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;text-indent:18pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;text-indent:18pt;line-height:1.5;\">、超市上货工</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;text-indent:18pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:12px;text-indent:18pt;line-height:1.5;\">收入：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;text-indent:18pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;text-indent:18pt;line-height:1.5;\">镑</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;text-indent:18pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">50</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;text-indent:18pt;line-height:1.5;\">便士</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;text-indent:18pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">-5</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;text-indent:18pt;line-height:1.5;\">镑</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;text-indent:18pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">50</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;text-indent:18pt;line-height:1.5;\">便士</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;text-indent:18pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">、英国当地餐馆，酒吧侍者</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">收入：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">镑</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">60</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">便士</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">-5</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">镑</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">50</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">便士</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">+</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">小费</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">;</span><o:p></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">、超市收银员</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">收入：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">镑</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">30</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">便士</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">-5</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">镑</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">;</span><o:p></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">、办公室，餐厅清洁工</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\"> (</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">早班</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">5AM-7AM </span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">晚班</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">8PM-9PM</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">，比较多〕</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">收入：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">镑</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">60</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">便士</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">-4</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">镑</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">20</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">便士</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">;</span><o:p></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">7</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">、办公室杂务人员</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\"> (</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">复印，打字，搬运库存文具，送邮件〕</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">收入：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">镑</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">60</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">便士</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">-4</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">镑</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">20</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">便士。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background:white;\">\r\n	<b></b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>','1','1','0');
INSERT INTO tbl_news VALUES('6',' 新政策之用于英国签证与移民的雅思考试解析','1428595200','upload/20151209/20151209173526_82157.jpg','','<p style=\"text-indent:18.0pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:9pt;\"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:18.0pt;background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">今年</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">20</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">日，英国政府宣布了签证类安全英语语言考试（</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">SELT</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">）的重要变动。如果同学们准备办理赴英居留或移民签证，需要了解由英国签证与移民局所颁布的调整政策。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">在申请多种签证类别时，您必须提交英国签证与移民局（</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">UK Visas and Immigration, UKVI</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">）认可的安全英语语言考试名单（简称</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">SELT</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">）中包括的英语考试成绩。雅思考试在此名单中。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">根据英国签证及移民局得官方文件通知，自</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">2015</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">年</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">日起，英国移民局只认可雅思考试和伦敦三一学院的语言考试。此次新政策针对英国所有需要提供语言测试的签证类型和</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">18</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">－</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">65</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">周岁的申请人。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:9pt;color:#000000;\">中国境内的申请人只能参加雅思考试来申请英国签证。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"text-indent:18pt;font-size:9pt;line-height:1.5;\">新正常发布后，适用于英国签证的雅思考试</span><span color:#595959;\"=\"\" style=\"text-indent: 18pt; font-size: 9pt; line-height: 1.5;\"> </span><span style=\"text-indent:18pt;font-size:9pt;line-height:1.5;color:#595959;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">已变更为</span><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#000000;\">三种类型</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000;\">：</span><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#000000;\">用于英国签证及移民的雅思培训类考试</span></strong></span><strong style=\"text-indent:18pt;line-height:1.5;\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:\'color:#595959;color:#000000;\">(IELTS UKVI Test)</span></strong><span style=\"text-indent:18pt;font-size:9pt;line-height:1.5;color:#595959;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">、</span><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#000000;\">用于英国签证与移民的雅思学术类考试</span></strong></span><strong style=\"text-indent:18pt;line-height:1.5;\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:\'color:#595959;color:#000000;\">(IELTS Academic)</span></strong><span style=\"text-indent:18pt;font-size:9pt;line-height:1.5;color:#595959;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">及</span><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#000000;\">雅思生活技能类考试</span></strong></span><strong style=\"text-indent:18pt;line-height:1.5;\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:\'color:#595959;color:#000000;\">(IELTSLife Skills)</span></strong><span style=\"text-indent:18pt;font-size:9pt;line-height:1.5;\">。</span><strong style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\" color:#00b050;\"=\"\">&nbsp;</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background:white;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;color:#E53333;\"><br />\r\n</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background:white;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;color:#E53333;\">三种考试区别：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;color:#3E3E3E;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background:white;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;\">⊙</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;\">用于英国签证及移民的雅思培训类考试</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;color:#3E3E3E;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;\">适用于英语国家移民申请，或申请培训及非文凭类课程，即用于英国所有要求提供语言测试成绩的签证申请<span>(</span>即将入读预科、语言班的课程，包括<span>Tier 4 </span>学生签证<span>)</span>。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background:white;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background:white;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;\">⊙</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;\">用于英国签证与移民的雅思学术类考试</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;color:#3E3E3E;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;\">适用于出国留学申请本科、研究生及以上学位，或获得专业资质。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background:white;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background:white;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;\">⊙</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;\">雅思生活技能类考试</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;color:#3E3E3E;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background:white;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;\">A1</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;\">级别</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background:white;\">\r\n	该考试旨在满足英国签证与移民局对于配偶<span>,</span>探亲类签证的申请者证明其英语听说能力的特定需求。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background:white;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;\">B1</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;\">级别</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background:white;\">\r\n	该考试旨在满足英国签证与移民局对于入籍，永居类等特定签证的申请者证明其英语听说能力的特定需求。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:9pt;\"></span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span> \r\n</p>','1','1','0');
INSERT INTO tbl_news VALUES('7','关于雅思考试有效证件的重要通知','1429200000','upload/20151210/20151210120009_60948.png','','<p style=\"background:white;text-indent:18pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:9pt;\"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">自2015年4月23日考试日期起，雅思考试、用于英国签证及移民的雅思考试、雅思生活技能类考试将不再接受任何形式的临时身份证及军人证件。特此提醒考生所有雅思考试网上报名及考试当天仅接受以下身份证件：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><strong>中国大陆考生</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">凭有效的二代身份证或护照报名并参加考试</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><strong>香港、澳门考生</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">凭有效的身份证或护照报名并参加考试</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">台湾考生</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">凭有效的台湾居民来往大陆通行证(台胞证)报名并参加考试</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">非中国籍考生</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">凭有效的护照报名</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">考生必须在考试当日出示与报名时完全一致的身份证件，且所出示证件上的个人信息(包括姓名、性别、出生日期、证件号码、证件有效期、证件签发机关)必须与报名时填写的信息完全一致，否则考生将被取消考试资格和考试成绩，并不得转考、退考或退费。请考生在报名时务必仔细核对。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">如果在考试日期前报名证件更改、丢失、过期、或由于其他不可抗力原因导致考试当天不能出示报名时使用的证件，请立即联系教育部考试中心雅思考试全国服务热线并服从相应安排。&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><strong> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background:white;text-indent:18pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:9pt;\"></span><span style=\"font-family:; font-size: 9pt;\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\"></span><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:9pt;\"></span><span style=\"font-family:; font-size: 9pt;\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\"></span><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:9pt;\"></span><span style=\"font-family:; font-size: 10pt;\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\"></span> \r\n</p>','1','1','0');
INSERT INTO tbl_news VALUES('8','淘优牌剁手党止血包！','1449414404','upload/20151206/20151206234634_31930.jpg','','<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align:center;margin-left:0cm;\">\r\n	<span style=\"white-space:nowrap;\">免费申请4所学校，外加2k奖学金，不能再多了……&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align:center;margin-left:0cm;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/kindeditor/attached/image/20151206/20151206164632_91653.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#7030A0;\"></span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;background:white;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#595959;\">告诉昨天刚剁完手的你们一个巨大福利，</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;background:white;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#595959;\">剁手节当天凡是</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#E36C09;\">递交所有材料</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#595959;\">至淘优</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#E36C09;\">，</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;background:white;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#E36C09;\">免费申请<span>4</span>所学校（<span>G5</span>学校除外），</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;background:white;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#E36C09;\">成功入学则返<span>2000</span>元奖学金！</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;background:white;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:red;\">申请不收钱！</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;background:white;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#E36C09;\">0</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#E36C09;\">风险！</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;background:white;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:red;\">0</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:red;\">费用！</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;background:white;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:red;\">简单粗暴，不开玩笑，爱心满满！</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;background:white;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:red;\">最重要的是还不用抢！</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\">&nbsp;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background:white;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#595959;\">你没有看错！！双</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;line-height:150%;color:#595959;\">11</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#595959;\">让我们</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;line-height:150%;color:#595959;\">High</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#595959;\">起来吧！</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#C00000;\">当天递交材料的学生，淘优免费为其申请四所学校，若学生成功入学，即返<span>2000</span>元奖学金！</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;\">还不快快行动起来！</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\">&nbsp;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#7030A0;\">What\r\nto do?</span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\">不要惊呆啦，赶紧回过神来整理好所有的材料，提前放上<span>“</span>购物车<span>”</span>，中国时间<span>11</span>月<span>11</span>日<span>00</span>：<span>00 - 23:59</span>期间发送给我们，就能领取奖学金啦！<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\">&nbsp;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:red;\">备注</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;color:red;\">:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\">1.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;\">此活动只针对从</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;color:#3E3E3E;\">2015</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;\">年</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;color:#3E3E3E;\">11</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;color:#3E3E3E;\">11</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;\">日起到</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;color:#3E3E3E;\">2016</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;\">年</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;color:#3E3E3E;\">12</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;color:#3E3E3E;\">31</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;\">日入学的申请，延期入学的不计入此计划</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;color:#3E3E3E;\">;</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;color:#3E3E3E;\">2. </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;\">时间截点以我们邮箱收到申请为准，其他方式递交的不计，请务必通过邮件发送；</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;\">3.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;\">淘优</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;\">保留此次活动的最终解释权。</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\">&nbsp;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;\">欲知更多更详细情况，请联系我们的咨询主管<span>:</span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\"></span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;\">Ben Huang</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;\">QQ</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#3E3E3E;\">:2029487993</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\">Email</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\">:\r\nx.huang@top-u.co.uk</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\">&nbsp;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#FFC000;\">公司介绍</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#FFC000;\"> Company\r\nIntroduction</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\">淘优英国留学成立于英国伦敦</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\">，</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\">是一间留学咨询服务公司。淘优以其优秀的英国本地文案、清一色留英硕士顾问团队和独特的英国<span>Top Up </span>项目申请而扬名海内外。此外，淘优英国留学也致力于为学生提供实习机会，帮助学生在申请前做好职业生涯规划，让他们更好地挖掘自身的潜力。<span></span></span> \r\n</p>','2','','');
INSERT INTO tbl_news VALUES('9','淘优携手分期乐，一年圆你学士梦！','1449415177','upload/20151206/20151206234327_96041.jpg','','<p align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:23.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:#F96E57;\">好</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;\">消息！淘优留学终于可以分期啦<span>~</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;\">同学们凭学生证即可在分期乐购买淘优留学服务，享受分期付款乐趣。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;\"><img src=\"/kindeditor/attached/image/20151206/20151206164326_94641.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;\"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:17.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#00B0F0;\">来！来！来<span style=\"background:yellow;\">!</span></span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#00B0F0;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<b> \r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<b style=\"font-size:12pt;line-height:1.5;\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt;color:#FFCA00;\">淘优 </span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;color:#F96E57;\">&amp; </span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;color:#5F9CEF;\">分期乐</span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;color:fuchsia;\">带你去留学</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;line-height:1.5;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;line-height:1.5;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-weight:normal;line-height:1.5;\"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:20.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:red;\">淘优携手分期乐，圆你一个本科梦<span>~</span></span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\"><br />\r\n</span><b><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#FFC000;\">【淘优英国留学】<span></span></span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#113567;\">营业时间：</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#403C3C;\">周一至周五<span>10</span>：<span>00-17:00</span>（周末上门需提前预约）<span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#113567;\">联系方式</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\">：<span>020</span>－<span>38921300/13427548208</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#113567;\">QQ</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\">：<span>1438928203</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#113567;\">详细地址</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\">：广州市天河区五山路<span>141</span>－<span>2</span>尚德大厦<span>A</span>座<span>1903</span></span><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#7030A0;\"></span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n</b> \r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>','2','','');
INSERT INTO tbl_news VALUES('10','华农大“Search行动”大赛完美落幕','1449415271','upload/20151206/20151206234116_75015.jpg','','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\">淘优教育讯&nbsp;<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span>日<span lang=\"EN-US\">19:00</span>－<span lang=\"EN-US\">21:00</span>华南农业大学社会工作协会在第三教学楼<span lang=\"EN-US\">212</span>举办“<span lang=\"EN-US\">search</span>行动”比赛决赛。参赛队伍通过<span lang=\"EN-US\">PPT</span>展示各自的研究成果，且生动形象的讲解了自己的想法和创意。现场座无虚席，气氛十分火爆，也说明了华农大学生对于发现自我、提升自我具有浓厚的兴趣与热爱。<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\">本次“大学生倡导大赛”已经完美落幕，相信通过这次“<span lang=\"EN-US\">Search</span>行动”，会有更多的大学生加入到发现自己身边问题的队伍中，并由此提升他们改变自我、提升自我、超越自我的能力。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\"><img src=\"/kindeditor/attached/image/20151206/20151206164105_79318.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>','2','','');
INSERT INTO tbl_news VALUES('11','华农大“Search行动”大赛开幕式','1449415375','upload/20151206/20151206233933_86501.jpg','','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\">淘优教育讯&nbsp;<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span>日<span lang=\"EN-US\">19</span>：<span lang=\"EN-US\">00</span>－<span lang=\"EN-US\">21</span>：<span lang=\"EN-US\">00 </span>，华农大<span lang=\"EN-US\">“Search</span>行动<span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span>大赛开幕式在教五<span lang=\"EN-US\">5B203</span>隆重举行。<span lang=\"EN-US\">“Search</span>行动<span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span>是由华南农业大学社会工作协会牵头，向全校报名的参赛队伍公开招标的活动。参赛队伍针对自己身边存在的问题提出自己的改善和倡导方法并写成一份竞标书，被评选出来进入决赛的竞标书有机会获得一定的经费和扩大自己的队伍，让更多的人参与进来，去实践自己的想法，使自己的倡导成为现实。而未被选上的队伍也可以重新加入到被选上队伍中一起实现共同的目标。广州市灯塔计划青少年发展促进会秘书长卢思歆老师、拜客广州总干事陈嘉俊老师、映诺社区发展机构传播官王颖老师出席了本次开幕式，并在现场进行<span lang=\"EN-US\">NGO</span>经验分享。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\">本次<span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span>大学生倡导大赛<span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span>诣在使更多的大学生加入到发现自己身边问题的队伍中，从而提升他们改变自我、提升自我、超越自我的能力。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\"><img src=\"/kindeditor/attached/image/20151206/20151206163930_84231.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>','2','','');
INSERT INTO tbl_news VALUES('12','华农大Search 行动 の 淘优国际教育现场咨询报名活动','1449415401','upload/20151206/20151206233541_61013.jpg','','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\">淘优教育讯&nbsp;<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">15-17</span>日<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>：<span lang=\"EN-US\">00 - 17</span>：<span lang=\"EN-US\">00</span>淘优国际教育携手华农大社会工作协会在芷园、西园、荷园举办现场咨询报名活动。同学们可以现场咨询英国、美国、加拿大留学项目。凡现场预约报名即可享九折优惠！<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\"><img src=\"/kindeditor/attached/image/20151206/20151206163745_53376.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>','2','','');
INSERT INTO tbl_news VALUES('13','英两大签证新政：访问签证允许度假和志愿服务','1429459200','upload/20151210/20151210120646_66630.jpg','','<p style=\"background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:9pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><strong>广州日报讯</strong>（记者</span></span><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:9pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">李琼）记者从英国驻华使领馆</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" helvetica\",\"sans-serif\";font-size:9pt;\"=\"\">/</span><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:9pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">文化教育处获悉，英国内政部简化到访英国的移民制度以吸引更多游客。主要变更包含将访问类别从</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" helvetica\",\"sans-serif\";font-size:9pt;\"=\"\">15</span><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:9pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">个减少到</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" helvetica\",\"sans-serif\";font-size:9pt;\"=\"\">4</span><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:9pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">个，重新调整学生访问类别并且提供简短、便利的移民政策指导以便更容易理解相关要求。这些变更将于</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" helvetica\",\"sans-serif\";font-size:9pt;\"=\"\">2015</span><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:9pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">年</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" helvetica\",\"sans-serif\";font-size:9pt;\"=\"\">4</span><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:9pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">月</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" helvetica\",\"sans-serif\";font-size:9pt;\"=\"\">24</span><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:9pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">日生效，并且将会为到访游客创建一个更加简单易用、灵活有效的系统。英国政府官网</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" helvetica\",\"sans-serif\";font-size:9pt;\"=\"\">GOV.uk</span><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:9pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">上的签证和移民页面也将于</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" helvetica\",\"sans-serif\";font-size:9pt;\"=\"\">2015</span><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:9pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">年</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" helvetica\",\"sans-serif\";font-size:9pt;\"=\"\">4</span><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:9pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">月</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" helvetica\",\"sans-serif\";font-size:9pt;\"=\"\">24</span><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:9pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">日进行修改。此外，从</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" helvetica\",\"sans-serif\";font-size:9pt;\"=\"\">2015</span><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:9pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">年</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" helvetica\",\"sans-serif\";font-size:9pt;\"=\"\">4</span><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:9pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">月</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" helvetica\",\"sans-serif\";font-size:9pt;\"=\"\">24</span><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:9pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">日起，所有的访问者都允许可以参加不超过</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" helvetica\",\"sans-serif\";font-size:9pt;\"=\"\">30</span><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:9pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">天的附带学习，此前，对于商务访问者和旅游访问者不可以参加。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:18pt;text-indent:18pt;font-size:9pt;color:#3E3E3E;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">变更之后将会有</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" helvetica\",\"sans-serif\";font-size:9pt;\"=\"\" style=\"line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 18pt; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\"><strong>4</strong></span><span style=\"line-height:18pt;text-indent:18pt;font-size:9pt;color:#3E3E3E;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><strong>个新的访问类别</strong>：</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background:white;\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\" helvetica\",\"sans-serif\";font-size:9pt;\"=\"\" style=\"line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 18pt; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">1.</span><span style=\"line-height:18pt;text-indent:18pt;font-size:9pt;color:#3E3E3E;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">普通访客：这将巩固现有的</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" helvetica\",\"sans-serif\";font-size:9pt;\"=\"\" style=\"line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 18pt; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">11</span><span style=\"line-height:18pt;text-indent:18pt;font-size:9pt;color:#3E3E3E;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">种访问类型签证包括普通访问者和商务访问者；</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background:white;\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\" helvetica\",\"sans-serif\";font-size:9pt;\"=\"\" style=\"line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 18pt; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">2.</span><span style=\"line-height:18pt;text-indent:18pt;font-size:9pt;color:#3E3E3E;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">将要在英国获取婚姻或者同性伴侣关系的访客；</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background:white;\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\" helvetica\",\"sans-serif\";font-size:9pt;\"=\"\" style=\"line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 18pt; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">3.</span><span style=\"line-height:18pt;text-indent:18pt;font-size:9pt;color:#3E3E3E;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">短期有偿工作访客；</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background:white;\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\" helvetica\",\"sans-serif\";font-size:9pt;\"=\"\" style=\"line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 18pt; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">4.</span><span style=\"line-height:18pt;text-indent:18pt;font-size:9pt;color:#3E3E3E;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">英国过境访客。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background:white;text-indent:17.25pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:small;\"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background:white;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:9pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">学生访问者和其他学生访问者将会被重新调整成为短期学生类别。这将更加明确此类签证是针对到英学习短期课程的访客。新的短期学生访问类别如下：短期学生访问</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" helvetica\",\"sans-serif\";font-size:9pt;\"=\"\">(</span><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:9pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">不超过</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" helvetica\",\"sans-serif\";font-size:9pt;\"=\"\">6</span><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:9pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">个月</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" helvetica\",\"sans-serif\";font-size:9pt;\"=\"\">)</span><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:9pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，适用于参加短期课程</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" helvetica\",\"sans-serif\";font-size:9pt;\"=\"\">(</span><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:9pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">包括英语语言学习</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" helvetica\",\"sans-serif\";font-size:9pt;\"=\"\">)</span><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:9pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的未成年和成年人；短期学生访问</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" helvetica\",\"sans-serif\";font-size:9pt;\"=\"\">(</span><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:9pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">不超过</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" helvetica\",\"sans-serif\";font-size:9pt;\"=\"\">11</span><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:9pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">个月</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" helvetica\",\"sans-serif\";font-size:9pt;\"=\"\">)</span><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:9pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，仅适用于参加不超过</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" helvetica\",\"sans-serif\";font-size:9pt;\"=\"\">11</span><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:9pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">个月英语语言课程学习的成年人。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background:white;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:18pt;text-indent:18pt;font-size:9pt;color:#3E3E3E;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">英国驻华使领馆</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" helvetica\",\"sans-serif\";font-size:9pt;\"=\"\" style=\"line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 18pt; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">/</span><span style=\"line-height:18pt;text-indent:18pt;font-size:9pt;color:#3E3E3E;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">文化教育处表示，减少访问类别将会消除相关复杂性，给游客在英活动更大的灵活性。例如，普通访问类别所签发的旅游签证同时也允许他们来度假，参加商务会议，进行附带研究，而不必申请单独类别的访问签证。访问者还可以在英国注册的慈善机构进行</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" helvetica\",\"sans-serif\";font-size:9pt;\"=\"\" style=\"line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 18pt; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">30</span><span style=\"line-height:18pt;text-indent:18pt;font-size:9pt;color:#3E3E3E;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">天的无偿志愿服务，而不需要工作类别的邀请方。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background:white;text-indent:17.25pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:small;\"> </span> \r\n</p>','1','1','0');
INSERT INTO tbl_news VALUES('14','出国留学行前体检的各项注意事项','1429632000','upload/20151211/20151211114112_84459.jpg','','<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:small;\"> </span> \r\n<p style=\"background:white;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;text-indent:18pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:9pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">出国留学的同学们，离境前的身体检查和免疫接种，也就是我们常说的体检也是需要注意的一项。否则，可能因为没有《国际预防接种证书》而被拒绝入境，或者因为缺少免疫证明而耽误入学。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:small;\"> </span> \r\n<p style=\"background:white;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;text-indent:18pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:9pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">如上所述，这里所讲的体检，包括两个部分：一是常说的在出入境检验检疫局所做的检查和疫苗接种；一是填写学校方面要求填写的疫苗接种历史表格。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:small;\"> </span> \r\n<p style=\"background:white;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;text-indent:18pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:9pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">首先，如果留学生想要顺利入境，需要去当地的出入境检验检疫局体检并接种疫苗。一般不需预约，只要在工作日的上午，带上两张两寸照片、身份证和护照以及笔前去。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:small;\"> </span> \r\n<p style=\"background:white;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:9pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">当然，和去医院体检一样，前一天不要吃太多油腻食物，晚上不要进食，并且第二天早上空腹前去接受检查。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:small;\"> </span> \r\n<p style=\"background:white;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;text-indent:18pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:9pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">另外，很多学校会要求学生填写有关疫苗注射历史的表格，这个表格也要随身携带，在检验检疫局交由医生填写、签字并盖章。如果是英文表格，不必担心医生会看不懂，他们都是比较专业的。因为需要知道学生的历史免疫记录，所以要记得携带学生从小到大的疫苗注射记录，这样可以顺利填写，避免重复注射</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" helvetica\",\"sans-serif\";font-size:9pt;\"=\"\">(</span><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:9pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">如果找不到之前的记录，学校又要求填写，那就需要再重新注射</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" helvetica\",\"sans-serif\";font-size:9pt;\"=\"\">)</span><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:9pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:small;\"> </span> \r\n<p style=\"background:white;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;text-indent:18pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:9pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">抵达出入境检验检疫局后，可先在大厅领取表格，填写后连同学校要求填写的表格一起交给医生，接下来就可以进行体检并根据个人实际情况安排免疫项目了。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:small;\"> </span> \r\n<p style=\"background:white;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;text-indent:18pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:9pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">体检方面，通常包括验血、内科、全身检查、</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" helvetica\",\"sans-serif\";font-size:9pt;\"=\"\">X</span><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:9pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">光透视等项目，费用在四五百元左右。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:small;\"> </span> \r\n<p style=\"background:white;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;text-indent:18pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:9pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">疫苗注射方面，如果学校没有特殊要求，医生会根据你前往的国家来给安排疫苗注射。例如，前往欧美国家，通常需要注射麻风腮三联疫苗，也就是麻疹、腮腺炎和风疹联合疫苗，也有地区还需要注射百日咳、白喉和破伤风的三联疫苗</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" helvetica\",\"sans-serif\";font-size:9pt;\"=\"\">;</span><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:9pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">前往卫生条件相对较差的国家，可能就需要注射霍乱、甲肝、伤寒等疫苗。如果学校方面有特殊要求，建议学生补齐所有疫苗，如果因为时间原因，部分疫苗的第二针或者第三针在国内来不及注射，和学校商议后，可在国外补上。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:small;\"> </span> \r\n<p style=\"background:white;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;text-indent:18pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:9pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">体检和疫苗注射结束后，学生可以在工作人员那里领取到一个通知单，上边会注明领取《国际旅行健康检查证明书》和《国际预防接种证书》的时间。通常前者在四五个工作日内就可以领取，如需加急，可以支付加急费用，并在当日领取。至于《国际预防接种证书》，也就是我们常说的</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" helvetica\",\"sans-serif\";font-size:9pt;\"=\"\">“</span><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:9pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">黄皮书</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\" helvetica\",\"sans-serif\";font-size:9pt;\"=\"\">”</span><span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:9pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，就要等待所有疫苗都注射完毕后，才能领取。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:small;\"> </span> \r\n<p style=\"background:white;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;text-indent:18pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:9pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">体检和疫苗注射流程都是出境必须的程序，是对他人的负责，更是对自己的负责。尤其学校方面，有了这个记录，一方面可以确保学生注射过所有疫苗；另一方面，在学生生病的时候，能够根据学生的注射记录和历史健康记录，来安排合适的治疗方案。所以，不论从哪个方面看，这一项对学生而言都是有好处的。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:small;\"> </span> \r\n<p style=\"background:white;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:black;font-size:9pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">英国留学的童鞋们要特别注意啦，去英国读书需要肺结核体检报告哦，记得要提早去办理。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:small;\"> </span>','1','1','0');
INSERT INTO tbl_news VALUES('15','英国将以最大幅度上调最低时薪！留学生们的福音！','1429804800','upload/20151210/20151210121051_30776.jpeg','','<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:small;\"> </span> \r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">英国政府近日宣布，从今年10月起，最低工资将增加3%（20便士），至每小时6.7英镑(约合62元人民币)，估计将有140万工人从中获益。据英国广播公司报道，该增长是7年来最大幅度的实质性工资水平上升，是由独立机构低收入委员会进行的建议。英国首相戴维·卡梅伦说，此举将全面提高“金融安全”以及给英国工人“一个更好的未来”。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">其中，学徒工的最低工资上升了20%或57便士，至每小时3.3英镑，但也有分析人士认为此增幅过高。工党则承诺大选成功后，将最终使最低工资上升至每小时8英镑以上。对于在英国留学的小伙伴来说，这无疑是巨大福利，去英国留学，又能省了一大笔钱哦，可以在网上给自己买两件好衣服啦。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">英国留学的同学们有很多人为了给家里减轻生活负担有打工的想法。在英国留学期间打工，不仅能缓解经济压力，还能得到能力上的锻炼。那么让我们深入了解下在英国打工必备的知识吧。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">* </span><strong><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">每周打工时间限制</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">作为热门的留学国家，英国制定了针对留学生的较为完善的打工政策。例如16岁以上可以打工，18岁以下每周打工时间不得超过10小时，18岁以上不超过20小时。寒暑假无限制。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">* </span><strong><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">打工还需要缴税</span></strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">留学生在英国打工期间还可享受除药费外的医疗全额保险。此外，在英国打工是需要交税的。假期里，每周打工超过20小时，需缴20%的税。因此，留学生在找到兼职工作后，需要及时向当地的Benefits\r\nAgency申请National Insurance Number（英国国家社会保险号），用于统计打工者的收入总额，以作为纳税的依据。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">* </span><strong><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">职位与工资</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">在工资方面，语言交流越流畅，能找到的高薪工资机会越大。所以童鞋们，练好英语是打工高薪必备武器，课余时间打工已成为留学生活的一部分。餐厅服务员、外卖员、销售员等职业在帮助留学生减轻经济负担的同时，也成为了他们人生中重要的一课。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:small;\"> </span>','1','1','0');
INSERT INTO tbl_news VALUES('16','2015年英国留学十大热门专业','1430064000','upload/20151210/20151210121613_95553.jpg','','<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:small;\"> </span> \r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">2015</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">英国留学的申请早已持续拉开序幕，有些大学的第一轮申请也宣告结束。而在申请中有些专业是经久不衰，一直受到众多留学生的追捧。留学专家给大家总结了下</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">15</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">年英国留学的十大热门专业：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><strong>1</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><strong>、传媒专业</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">英国传媒专业主要有三个方向：一是大众传媒，主要学习传播、广告、新闻写作、报道及采访等</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">;</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">二是影视制作媒体，包括编辑、游戏设计、音效处理、广告设计及电影电视制作等</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">;</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">三是媒体及记者，主要包括杂志社、报社、影视和新闻机构等。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">英国拥有着世界最大的新闻广播机构</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">BBC</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">、有全世界著名的通讯社路透社、有世界发行量最大的报纸等，均使得英国在全球传媒产业中地位举足轻重。毕业生就业领域包括网站、电视台、电台、报社、杂志社等。</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">2012</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">伦敦奥运会的举办更是提升了传媒专业的火热度，预计未来传媒专业依然是英国国内外学生的专业热门首选。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><strong>2</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><strong>、翻译口译专业</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">随着中国同世界各国在政治、经济、文化等各领域往来日益增多，各类外事活动频繁举行，很多场合都迫切需要翻译技巧娴熟的翻译人才以确保各方沟通顺畅，同时，对翻译从业者素质的要求也在逐步提高。近年来，英国翻译类硕士课程已逐渐成为许多准留学生的目标。其中，欧盟同传学位机构、国际口笔译高等教育机构常设会议、国际会议口译员协会等都与英国较优秀的翻译类院校保持着较为紧密的关系。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><strong>3</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><strong>、会计与金融专业</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">英国金融业非常发达，金融业的发展也带动了会计领域的飞速前进。英国是最早出现职业会计师、第一个建立现代意义上会计职业团体的国家，总部设在英国的特许公认会计师公会是目前世界上领先的专业会计师团体，也是国际学员最多、规模发展最快的专业会计师组织，因此去英国学习会计有得天独厚的优势，而且利于就业。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">金融专业主要教授金融理论知识和财务管理知识，目的是培养学生对各类金融市场、金融产品的了解和操作。会计专业主要教授学生如何有效记录和深入理解某机构的财务状况，目的是培养学生通过账面信息了解相应机构，从而有效做出价值判断或给出商业建议。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">在英国，会计学的全称为</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">MSc Accounting&amp;Finance</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">，它涉及到会计、财政、税收、金融、保险、工商企业管理等专业的内容，一直都是留学英国的学生选择最多的科目之一。目前，会计专业就业形势很好，被称为外资企业、跨国公司的</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">“</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">香饽饽</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">”</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">。外资企业和跨国公司倾向于选择有海外留学背景或持有国际执业资格证书的人才。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><strong>4</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><strong>、艺术专业</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">英国是艺术氛围浓厚，许多美术馆或博物馆可免费参观，且每年举行很多的艺术节，比如非常著名的爱丁堡艺术节。英国有许多著名的艺术类院校，英国的艺术类专业在世界也属一流，因此，艺术类考生去英国留学是非常好的选择。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">英国有很多设计类课程可以考虑，如：平面设计、产品设计、服装设计、珠宝设计等。同时也有商科和艺术课程结合的课程，如时尚推广、时尚管理等。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><strong>5</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><strong>、建筑学</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">英国是建筑学的集大成圣地，聚集了世界众多的建筑风格：英国议会大厦为代表的浪漫主义风格、伦敦不列颠博物馆为代表的古典复兴主义风格、威斯敏斯特大教堂为典型的哥特式风格等，这些迥然不同的建筑风格，体现了英国建筑学的前沿地位。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">在英国，学生想获得建筑师资格证并非易事，需经过英国皇家建筑师学会和建筑师注册委员会认可，并在建筑师事务所实习至少两年，虽然严格但是收入颇丰。英国大学建筑学开设的课程主要有：设计理论与实践、建筑环境设计、环境与科技、建筑管理与实践、计算机辅助建筑设计等。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><strong>6</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><strong>、服装设计专业</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">服装、时尚专业在一阵阵潮流更新中越来越显示出自己的优势，而英国正好走在时尚的前沿，成为了众多留学生追求的目标。</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">英国有很多大家广为喜爱的时尚品牌，并且伦敦时装周以另类服装设计概念、奇异展出形式的时尚设计，吸引留学生更加青睐于到英国就读服装管理、时尚管理等专业，英国也因此成为想要深造服装、时尚专业的学生的首选地之一。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><strong>7</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><strong>、精算专业</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">未来几年精算师会随着国际保险巨头在中国开拓市场以及国内企业的需要和人们对于保险认识的加强，成为保险业最炙手可热的人才。因此，精算行业也成为众多留学生梦想领略到的魅力风景。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><strong>8</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><strong>、计算机科学</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">英国的教育机构在开发计算机系统和新型应用软件方面一直处于领先地位，英国的计算机专家在集成电路、电讯、互联网、逻辑电路、人工智能和电子科学方面取得了很多创新成果。同时，英国大学计算机专业与国内外各大公司紧密合作，培养储备人才。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">计算机科学是一门包含各种与计算和信息处理相关主题的系统学科，从抽象的算法分析、形式化语法到编程语言、程序设计、软件和硬件等，所覆盖的专业包括：计算机通信、网络安全、人工智能、多媒体技术、软件开发、信息系统等。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><strong>9</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><strong>、电气工程专业</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">英国的电气工程可谓是欧洲一流、世界领先，重要的电子电气厂商如</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">Silicon Radio</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">、</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">Wolfson</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">、</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">Filtronic</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">、</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">REED</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">等都起源于英国。毕业生就业方向为电力设计研究院、电力电子类高新技术企业、高等院校、科研院所等。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">英国电气工程专业的教育理念极具前瞻性和创造性，学生可以充分掌握创造思维和尖端技术设计理念。电气工程是电气与电子并重，电力电子与信息电子相融，软件与硬件兼备，装置与系统结合的一门学科。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><strong>10</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><strong>、土木工程专业</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;line-height:18pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">去英国学习土木工程专业有两大优势：一是英国开设土木工程学科的院校都经过协调小组及联合评估小组核准，确保了教学质量</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">;</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">二是土木工程专业常与其它相关学科如环境工程、建筑工程等结合，学生有机会兼修其他专业并获得到国内外实地考察及交流的机会。</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">木工程是研究如何应用科学原理和数学规划、施工和维护各种建筑和设施的学科，研究方向主要为：结构工程、交通工程、环境工程、水利工程、建设工程等。课程设置主要为：工程力学、岩土力学、地基与基础、工程地质学、工程水文学、工程制图、建筑材料、混凝土结构、工程机构、施工技术与管理等。</span> \r\n</p>','1','1','0');
INSERT INTO tbl_news VALUES('17','赴英签证审核时间 将由15天缩至6天','1430236800','upload/20151211/20151211113758_25031.jpg','','<p style=\"background:white;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:9pt;color:#3E3E3E;line-height:1.5;\">重庆商报讯</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">未来，市民前往英国将更加方便，其签证审核时间将从原来的</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">15</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">个工作日缩至</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">个工作日。昨日，英国首位女驻华大使吴百纳访渝，她表示，重庆与英国合作关系密切，将加大文教、商贸、科研等方面的合作。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">吴百纳说，为了更好地服务中国游客，英国在中国的签证中心，都增加了办事人员提高了效率，从申请人提交签证申请之日算起，到签证官最终决定是否发放签证，从原来的</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">15</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">个工作日，缩减到了</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">个工作日，而且普通赴英访问签证（</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">个月期），由人民币</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">830</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">元微调至</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">850</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">元，仅比之前涨了</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">20</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">元。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">另外，重庆地区还开通了签证加急办理的快捷服务。如果需要加急办理签证，除正常办理费用外，申请人还要额外支付费用</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">520</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">元，加急快捷服务一般会在</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">个工作日内返还护照。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">吴百纳说，今年是中英文化交流年，同时也是英国驻重庆总领馆设立</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">15</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">周年，为此，将开展系列文化交流活动。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">据英国驻重庆总领馆提供的活动目录显示，在</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">5~6</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">月，将推送英国最新的</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">10</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">支单曲，邀请市民评选最喜爱的歌曲，参与者有机会前往英国参加知名的</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">Bestival</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">音乐之旅。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">而最值得市民期待的是，在</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">月，将举办英国电影巡展。通过一系列首映、访谈和现场活动，将英国最优秀的电影作品展示给市民。电影既有修复版的经典电影，又有创新作品。</span> \r\n</p>','1','1','0');
INSERT INTO tbl_news VALUES('18','留学问答：英国一年制硕士的含金量','1431273600','upload/20151211/20151211114840_08436.jpg','','<p style=\"vertical-align:baseline;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><strong>Q</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><strong>：国内硕士要两到三年，美国硕士也要两年，而英国硕士只要一年，会不会出现含金量不如其它国家的问题？另外，一直有个说法是国内很多单位会更认可国内的研究生、博士生，会不会有留学回来不受重视的情况？</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"vertical-align:baseline;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><strong>很多计划前往英国留学的中国学生都有这样的顾虑，在大家的概念中，其它国家都需要二至三年完成硕士学业，为什么英国只需要一年？</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"vertical-align:baseline;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"vertical-align:baseline;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">A</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">: 其实，大家大可放心。虽然英国硕士的学制只有一年，但是课业相当紧张，安排得也很满。比如传媒专业，基本一个学期就有5门左右的必修课，每个月每门课都要交一篇小论文（essay），而且基本每周都要准备一次演讲（presentation）。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"vertical-align:baseline;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">千万不要觉得可以像在国内一样临时抱佛脚，不然的话就有可能过不了。总之，基本在这一年，常常泡在图书馆是肯定的，学习的强度也是比较大的，绝对不会让你有学习不够的感觉。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"vertical-align:baseline;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">不过英国也有一些不太正规的院校，核实这个很简单，有疑问的同学可以到中华人民共和国教育涉外监管信息网查询。符合标准的院校，都是在国内承认的。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"vertical-align:baseline;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">驻伦敦中国大使馆的高级官员也曾表示，从来没有收到过关于一年制硕士学历不被承认的信息。如果消息确实存在的话，大使馆会在第一时间向社会发出官方文件。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"vertical-align:baseline;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">英国文化协会（British Council）中国区的高层也表示，英国一年制硕士不被承认的说法，是不真实的。因为中英两国政府，签订过两国教育学位互认协议。中国不可能会单方面违背协议，做出影响两国文化教育交流的行为。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"vertical-align:baseline;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">其实硕士到底读几年，国际上并没有一个硬性的标准。英国、新加坡等国家的绝大部分专业都是一年制的。在澳洲，硕士有1年、1.5年、2年的。美国其实也有1年制的硕士专业。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"vertical-align:baseline;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">其实时间不是问题，对比各国的教育体制学分，英国一年硕士所修的学分完全等同于其它国家的硕士学分。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"vertical-align:baseline;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">但是毕业回国就业的话，每家单位的情况就不太一样了。有些单位的确不太青睐从国外毕业的留学生，基本上都会追问大学本科的学历和成绩。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"vertical-align:baseline;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">但有些公司，比如外企，或者工作需要常和国外公司打交道的，又或者需要英文写作的岗位就会比较青睐国外留学生，有的招聘时会特别注明：有留学经历的优先。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"vertical-align:baseline;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">所以各花入各眼，只要你有能力，请相信一定有公司欣赏你、录用你。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><strong>转载自：BBC</strong></span> \r\n</p>','1','1','0');
INSERT INTO tbl_news VALUES('19','用于英国签证及移民的雅思考试及雅思生活技能类考试7-9月开放报名','1431446400','upload/20151211/20151211114503_93993.jpg','','<p style=\"background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">用于英国签证及移民的雅思考试及雅思生活技能类考试7月至9月的考位已开放报名。即日起，您可以在教育部考试中心雅思考试报名网站指定的中国大陆地区12个考场注册7月-9月的用于英国签证及移民的雅思考试及雅思生活技能类考试。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><strong>*</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><strong>2015</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><strong>年</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><strong>7</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><strong>月至</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><strong>9</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><strong>月</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><strong>用于</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><strong>英国签证及移民的雅思考试</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><strong>考试报名截止日期、准考证打印日期和成绩单寄送日期</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">\r\n	<table style=\"width:100%;\" cellpadding=\"2\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"1\" bordercolor=\"#000000\">\r\n		<tbody>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">考试日期</span><br />\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">类别</span><br />\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">报名截止日期</span><br />\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">准考证打印日期</span><br />\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">成绩单寄送日期</span><br />\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">04/07/2015</span><br />\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">A</span><br />\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">10/06/2015</span><br />\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">24/06/2015</span><br />\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">17/07/2015</span><br />\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">11/07/2015</span><br />\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">A+G</span><br />\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">17/06/2015</span><br />\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">01/07/2015</span><br />\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">24/07/2015</span><br />\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">23/07/2015</span><br />\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">A+G</span><br />\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">30/06/2015</span><br />\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">13/07/2015</span><br />\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">05/08/2015</span><br />\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">25/07/2015</span><br />\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">A</span><br />\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">02/07/2015</span><br />\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">15/07/2015</span><br />\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">07/08/2015</span><br />\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">01/08/2015</span><br />\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">A+G</span><br />\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">09/07/2015</span><br />\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">22/07/2015</span><br />\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:12px;\">14/08/</span> \r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</tbody>\r\n	</table>\r\n</p>','1','1','0');
INSERT INTO tbl_news VALUES('20','英国留学“说话术”：给课堂上插不上话的留学党们','1432224000','upload/20151218/20151218145103_15845.jpg','','<p style=\"background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#c00000;\"=\"\">“ </span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;color:#595959;\">相信不少小伙伴们刚来英国的时候，都经历过一件比较痛苦的事：上课发言插不上话。很多时候，答案已经了然于胸，就是开不了口。有的同学可能是因为英语本身不好，有的是因为不好意思开口，还有的是在组织语言的时候人家已经下一个问题了</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#595959;\"=\"\">......</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;color:#595959;\">所以，在英国课上</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#595959;\"=\"\">“</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;color:#595959;\">插话</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#595959;\"=\"\">”</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;color:#595959;\">，也是一门学问。</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#c00000;\"=\"\">”</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;color:#3E3E3E;\">英国有自己的说话术，但我们在中国不管学了多少年英语，对这套说话术，仍毫无了解。稍微礼貌点句子的就只会说</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\">\"Could you …please?\" </span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;color:#3E3E3E;\">殊不知，这个用法是不够礼貌和客气的，虽然是问句，虽然里面有</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\">\"please\"</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;color:#3E3E3E;\">，但还是一种要求的和轻微命令的语气。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;color:#3E3E3E;\">刚到英国的时候，最痛苦的事情莫过于上课发言：插不上话。虽然英国人在侃的那些内容有些很浅显不是什么真知灼见，但是他们就是在那里滔滔不绝。有你举手的功夫，或者你在头脑中组织语言的时间，人家已经侃了半天了。如果是你是学文科和社科的专业，这种情况你肯定不陌生。</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;line-height:1.5;\">&nbsp;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;color:#3E3E3E;\">在英国，不兴举手，只需要一个手势（抬下手）或者一个声音（</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\">Ummm,Yeah, Well</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;color:#3E3E3E;\">之类的）把别人的注意力吸引过来即可开讲。一堆同学之间要讲</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\">N</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;color:#3E3E3E;\">个回合老师才说话。这个时候，如果你加入到一个对话，就非常需要承上启下，需要和别人互动，需要总结别人的话，需要明确的表达自己的话和前面一个或者几个人的话之间是什么逻辑关系。这种逻辑关系可以是：补充，反对，支持，提问要求澄清</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\">......</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background:white;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background:white;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;\">那么在英国课堂上该怎么讲话，怎么开始，怎么反驳，怎么提问呢？接下来，小编将和大家分享一下课堂上的</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:;\" \"=\"\">“</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;\">说话术</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:;\" \"=\"\">” </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;\">～</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:9pt;line-height:1.5;\">&nbsp;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background:white;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#E36C09;\">★表达自己意见</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">- I think that... * </span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">最简单的</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><br />\r\n- It seems to me that... * </span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">可以用作表达意见，或者</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">summarize</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">或者</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">confirm</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">对方说的话。</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><br />\r\n- I would argue that...* </span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">这里面用</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">would</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">来弱化语气。</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><br />\r\n- Just to go along with what you said... * </span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">真的很好用，承上启下。这句话还好在，它使你现在插话看上去</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">legitimate</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">，因为你是为了和前面的那个人</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">go along</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">啊。不赶紧接话，不就</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">along</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">不上了嘛。</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><br />\r\n- Going back to what xxx said... * </span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">同上。不过一般是你已经说了几句，此事，想要</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">relate to someting </span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">别人刚刚提到过或者蜻蜓点水说道的东西。这句话的好处就是，一能</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">bring others on board</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">说看我的说法和你是有一致之处的，</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">二能表现他刚才说的东西你还有印象。</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#c00000;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;color:#E36C09;\">★</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#E36C09;\">同意或者反对</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#c00000;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">- I agree with you. * </span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">最简单的</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><br />\r\n- Building on what XX has just said, ....<br />\r\n- I am with you..., but [main point]. * </span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">这里</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">I\r\nam with you</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">不一定表示同意也不一定表示反对，它主要的意思是说</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">“</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">你说的我听懂了</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">/</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">我跟上你说的了。</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">”<br />\r\n- I follow your logic, but have you thought about/considered this... [main\r\npoint]...? * </span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">和上面一句话的逻辑是一样的：</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">“</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">你说的我明白了，但是</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">...”<br />\r\n- I see what you are saying, but I’m not sure I would argue that... * </span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">和上面两句话的逻辑一样。</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><br />\r\n- With all due respect, I think...</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#c00000;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#E36C09;\">★</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#E36C09;\">谦虚地反对</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#c00000;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Correct me if I’m wrong, but\r\nisn’t [a different topic]...?<br />\r\n- I’m not an expert on..., it seems to me that...<br />\r\n- I might be wrong, but ...<br />\r\n- I suspect that I lack some information about this aspect, but here is my two\r\ncents.<br />\r\n- I am not sure about this..., you might want to check with Professor X...\r\nWould you mind letting me know what he/she says?<br />\r\n- [</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">别人说了一堆之后</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">] This is one way to look at it.\r\nAnother way to look at it might be....</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#c00000;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#E36C09;\">★</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#E36C09;\">疑惑追问</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#c00000;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Just to clarify,...<br />\r\n- May I ask a follow-up question?<br />\r\n- Could you say more (about it)? *</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">不确定自己是不是听懂了，请别人多解释一些。</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><br />\r\n- Could you elaborate on this?</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#c00000;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#E36C09;\">★</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#E36C09;\">会议报告、演讲之后提问</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#c00000;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">- That’s an amazing model/useful\r\nconcept, but it occurred to me that [this/something] might also play a\r\nrole....Have you considered ...?<br />\r\n- Thanks for your talk. I completely agree with your conclusion, but as I’m\r\nsure you’re aware, Dr. XX explains this in a different way, and I was wondering\r\nif you could address her theory. * “but as I’m sure you’re aware”</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">完全是给对方一个台阶下，可能那个理论他根本没有考虑过。但是如果对方是很</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">senior</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">的，我们也需要客套一下。</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#c00000;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#E36C09;\">★</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#E36C09;\">需求帮助</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#c00000;\"=\"\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">- I was wondering if I could talk\r\nto you about... *</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">一般都是用过去时，在</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">email</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">里面也是如此。而且，虽然</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">was wondering/hoping</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">这种进行时看起来很怪，但是用法就是这样子的。</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><br />\r\n- I was hoping that if I could talk to you about...<br />\r\n- I was wondering if it’d be possible that you...*<br />\r\n- Sorry to bother you, Professor X....<br />\r\n- I realize this is an unusual request...<br />\r\n- I realize that you are very busy...<br />\r\n- Thanks for your time.<br />\r\n- Thanks in advance for your help.<br />\r\n- It would be great if you could...*</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">这个是最常用的，尤其是</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">email</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">里面。</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\" color:#3e3e3e;\"=\"\"></span> \r\n</p>','1','1','0');
INSERT INTO tbl_news VALUES('21','英国留学面签攻略，助你顺利通过面签关 ','1434556800','upload/20151218/20151218145355_27389.jpg','','<p>\r\n	<strong><span>英国留学签证官希望了解的问题：</span></strong><br />\r\n<span> 1</span><span>、留学生到英国留学的目的、是否有正规学校的入学通知、学生的身份是否属实。</span><br />\r\n<span> 2</span><span>、留学生是否有足够的经济能力负担自己在英国留学期间的各种费用。</span><br />\r\n<span> 3</span><span>、留学生是否有移民倾向、是否有回国计划、是否有长期规划及回国后是否会从事与专业相关的工作。</span><br />\r\n<span><strong>英国留学面签时应注意：</strong></span><br />\r\n<span>★</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span><strong>表达方式要清晰</strong></span><br />\r\n<span>英国留学签证申请过程中因精神紧张而出现口误的情况很普遍，通常表现为与英国签证申请官对话含混不清、或词不达意、或讲话断续支吾又或眼神游移不定等。</span><span>因此，学生面试之前就对签证官的提问有一个初步了解，并增强自己的对话能力，使签证官在和你交谈之后能够做出清晰的判断。</span><br />\r\n<span>★</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span><strong>不要有移民倾向</strong></span><br />\r\n<span>要有合理的英国留学计划，没有移民倾向并且计划学成回国，是能够保障获得英国签证申请的条件之一。</span><br />\r\n<span>此外，要对自己未来的发展阐述明晰，让签证官听得清楚，而不是被认为你会移民留在英国工作，否则就会增加拒签风险。</span><br />\r\n<span>★</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span><strong>心态要放端正</strong></span><br />\r\n<span>心态平和，对拒签要有理性的认识，要把申请签证当作对自身素质的考验，抱着平和的心态有助于自然发挥，也可以在不利的情况下扭转局面，在面签进行困难，或已有签证局面出现不利的情况下，更需沉着应战。</span><br />\r\n<span>这时需抱着</span><span>“</span><span>置死地而后生</span><span>”</span><span>的心态，继续面签的过程，状态放松之后，往往会有峰回路转，申请人超水平发挥的情况出现，最后出奇制胜地获得签证。</span><br />\r\n<span>★</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span><strong>面对面试官要自信</strong></span><br />\r\n<span>自信不是要盛气凌人，是一种平和、稳重的态度。和签证官对话时，要以一种交流的语气和他谈话。</span><br />\r\n<span>不可以畏畏缩缩，紧张，否则会给签证官一种紧张、抵触的感觉。当然，这一点是建立在坚固的背景和充分的准备上的。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span>下面，就让我们来了解下英国面签的<strong>常见问题</strong>：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#E56600;\"><strong>一、基本情况：</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> 1. Are you fit and well enough to be interviewed?</span><br />\r\n<span> 2. Is this your application form? Do you understand it and did you sign it ?</span><br />\r\n<span> 3. And how long? What is the maximum time you wish to stay there?</span><br />\r\n<span> 4. Are you traveling along or with someone else?</span><br />\r\n<span> 5. Do you know anyone at all in the UK?</span><br />\r\n<span> 6. Is any of your family outside China now/? If so, who are they and where?</span><br />\r\n<span> 7. Do you know anyone who intends to study in the UK?</span><br />\r\n<span> 8. Do you know anyone you know refused a visa to go to the UK?</span><br />\r\n<span> 9.Are you one of any political parties in China?</span><br />\r\n<span> 10. Have you ever applies for a visa to go to any other country?</span><br />\r\n<span> 11. Is this your first tine applying for a visa?</span><br />\r\n<span> 12. Is this the first time going out of the China?</span><br />\r\n<span> 13. Why do you want to go to the UK?</span><br />\r\n<span> 14. What will you do in the UK?</span><br />\r\n<span> 15. Why do you intend to study in the UK rather than China?</span><br />\r\n<span> 16. What degree will you plan to pursue in the UK?</span><br />\r\n<span> 17. Do you think UK has some more advantage than other countries?</span><br />\r\n<span> 18. When you have the idea to go abroad to study ?</span><br />\r\n<span> 19. Do you know about UK?</span><br />\r\n<span> 20. When will you arrive in UK?</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:#E56600;\"><strong>二、出国目的：</strong></span><br />\r\n<span> 1. What is your future plan? What will you do after graduation?</span><br />\r\n<span> 2. Wold you come back after graduation?</span><br />\r\n<span> 3. What degree do you intend to achieve after graduation?</span><br />\r\n<span> 4. Will you want to settle in the UK?</span><br />\r\n<span> 5. After graduation, will you plan to find a job in the UK?</span><br />\r\n<span> 6. In the UK, you will earn much money than in China. Then why do you say you\r\nwill come back to China?</span><br />\r\n<span> 7. If a company wants to hire you after graduation, would you come?</span><br />\r\n<span> 8. What do you think your future position after your study?</span><br />\r\n<span> 9. And what do you think your future salary?</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:#E56600;\"><strong>三、学习计划篇：</strong></span><br />\r\n<span> 1. Where will you study ?</span><br />\r\n<span> 2. How did you know this University?</span><br />\r\n<span> 3. How much do you know this University?</span><br />\r\n<span> 4. Which subject will you study /?what is your proposed course?</span><br />\r\n<span> 5. Which course will you study? what is the course arrangement? How much do you\r\nknow about your course?</span><br />\r\n<span> 6. How many hours will you study per hour?</span><br />\r\n<span> 7. When is the opeing date of school term?</span><br />\r\n<span> 8. Where are you going to live in UK?</span><br />\r\n<span> 9. Do you need use English in your study?</span><br />\r\n<span> 10. Do you have to take the English Course?</span><br />\r\n<span> 11. Have you ever considered other school while applying ? What are they?</span><br />\r\n<span> 12. Then why do you choose this University?</span><br />\r\n<span> 13. Why do you choose Food Production Management? Why do you want to study Food\r\nProduction Management?</span><br />\r\n<span> 14. What is your last degree obtained?</span><br />\r\n<span> 15. When did you graduate?</span><br />\r\n<span> 16. What do you do now? what have you studied?</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:#E56600;\"><strong>四、资金证明和来源：</strong></span><br />\r\n<span> 1. What are your tuition fees?</span><br />\r\n<span> 2. What about the living expenses? In addition to tuition?</span><br />\r\n<span> 3. Do you know how much money does it cost for the entire period of your study?</span><br />\r\n<span> 4. Is the found available ? how much?</span><br />\r\n<span> 5. Does it include the stocks?</span><br />\r\n<span> 6. Where does the money come from? Who will pay for the money ?Who will pay\r\nyour courses?</span><br />\r\n<span> 7. What is their annual income? What is your parents salary?</span><br />\r\n<span> 8. What do your parents do? How can they supported you?How does the money come\r\nfrom?</span><br />\r\n<span> 9. Can you give some description of your father’s company? Can you give some\r\ndescription of your mother’s company?</span><br />\r\n<span> 10. Can I look at your bankbook?</span><br />\r\n<span> 11. Can I look at your bank certification?</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span>在你面签之后，无论签是否拿到签证，都建议你立刻拿起笔，把你签证过程中的所有问题及你如何回答的都记下来，如果你拿到签证，就一切</span><span>OK</span><span>！</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span>如果你被拒签或撤签，这些问题就更重要了，因为你每说的一句话和你所有的材料在使馆都有记录的，童鞋们可以根据自己面试的问题分析是否能再签及如何再签。</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">例如，一位被南安普顿大学录取的孩纸就是这样，在面签后遭拒，最后回忆起是因为面签太紧张，资金这一块有口误。知道拒签原因后再签就能更有胜算。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#E53333;\"><strong>面签新政之应对良策：</strong></span><br />\r\n<span><strong>1</strong></span><span><strong>、全面掌握相关信息</strong></span><br />\r\n<span>切忌掌握最新的</span><span>“</span><span>面签流程</span><span>”</span><span>、面签新闻和注意事项等信息。从多方面了解英国国家、自己所选择的院校及学习领域的相关知识。关注其他童鞋的面签经验以作参考。</span><br />\r\n<span><strong>2</strong></span><span><strong>、提高英语表达能力</strong></span><br />\r\n<span>充分利用时间制定一个适合自己的英语巩固计划，努力提高英语表达能力。向签证官展现出素质优异的准留学生形象。</span><br />\r\n<span><strong>3</strong></span><span><strong>、叙述表达清晰</strong></span><br />\r\n<span>清晰表达自己在国内的学习及生活情况，不要过多关注语言或者语法错误。在面试过程中，如果语言表达出错也不要慌张，稍作情绪整理后，按照之前的思路继续作答即可。</span><br />\r\n<span><strong>4</strong></span><span><strong>、准时参加面试</strong></span><br />\r\n<span>接到面试通知的申请者切勿缺席面试，否则签证申请将会自动被拒绝，也不要迟到，以免影响面试官对申请者的印象。如果有特殊情况无法参加面试，请马上联系签证中心申请改期。</span><br />\r\n<span><strong>5</strong></span><span><strong>、注重礼仪和礼貌</strong></span><br />\r\n<span>参加面签要注重自己的装扮、穿着要干净整齐，可以穿得稍微正式些。在面试时要注重礼貌，打招呼时要用敬语。态度应端正认真，切忌吊儿郎当。</span><br />\r\n<span><strong>6</strong></span><span><strong>、提前申请签证</strong></span><br />\r\n<span>最好提前办理签证，以免因签证审理的延误而错过入学。假如被抽到进行面试，申请人也无需过分紧张，只要保持良好放松的心态，保证递交的材料真实无误就可以了。</span> \r\n</p>','1','1','0');

